data.description: Unbeatable Single-Level Living in Lompoc!This gated beauty is your ticket to 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and over 1500 sq ft of pure convenience in a sought-after community. Sun-drenched living spaces welcome you, complete with a cozy fireplace for those snug nights in.Whip up brunch in the spacious kitchen, boasting a charming breakfast nook and ample space for culinary creativity. With soaring ceilings, easy-care laminate flooring, and Berber carpeting, comfort meets style at every turn.Outside, your entertainment oasis awaits, featuring low-maintenance pavers and stained concrete for endless gatherings under the sun.Ideally situated near shopping, schools, and Vandenberg Space Force Base, this single-level haven won't linger long on the market at this unbeatable price. Don't delay--schedule your showing today!
